354
00:21:25,660 --> 00:21:27,160
and it's so pretty!

355
00:21:28,760 --> 00:21:31,759
So this was what he was talking about!

356
00:21:31,760 --> 00:21:33,759
What?

357
00:21:33,760 --> 00:21:34,959
The light of dawn seeps through.

358
00:21:34,960 --> 00:21:37,059
The light of the sunset shines on 2,000 such jars

359
00:21:37,060 --> 00:21:40,559
filled with 1,000 gold coins.

360
00:21:40,560 --> 00:21:42,059
This is a nursery song! Kurogane means iron!

361
00:21:42,060 --> 00:21:45,459
In other words, this lake is an iron jar.

362
00:21:45,460 --> 00:21:47,959
When the sunrise and sunset shine on the lake,

363
00:21:47,960 --> 00:21:49,759
it glitters gold, and the ripple of the waters

364
00:21:49,760 --> 00:21:51,759
look as if gold coins had been scattered.

365
00:21:51,760 --> 00:21:54,160
That's what the song meant.

366
00:21:58,960 --> 00:22:01,160
That's not what I came here for.

367
00:22:07,960 --> 00:22:11,559
Until we went to Ebisu Bridge, I didn't realize it but...

368
00:22:11,560 --> 00:22:15,259
It seems as if I...

369
00:22:15,260 --> 00:22:17,460
You know... sort of like... you know about you...

370
00:22:18,460 --> 00:22:21,059
All civilians evacuate to a safe place!

371
00:22:21,060 --> 00:22:23,059
What?

372
00:22:23,060 --> 00:22:26,060
We will begin strategy for capturing the Nue as of now!

373
00:22:29,360 --> 00:22:31,859
Self Defense Force?

374
00:22:31,860 --> 00:22:33,460
They really came!

375
00:22:38,860 --> 00:22:40,559
Well, if they're coming it's probably the air force

376
00:22:40,560 --> 00:22:43,459
from the Hamamatsu Air Force Base?

377
00:22:43,460 --> 00:22:46,360
And? What about me?

378
00:22:48,660 --> 00:22:50,859
Just like you said,

379
00:22:50,860 --> 00:22:53,859
I mixed the egg and the porridge tasted delicious.

380
00:22:53,860 --> 00:22:55,559
Just an uninteresting story.

381
00:22:55,560 --> 00:22:59,760
Right? Porridges taste better if you mix them?

382
00:23:02,760 --> 00:23:04,760
Ran!

383
00:23:06,860 --> 00:23:09,359
What did Heiji say to you?

