00:23:09,360 --> 00:23:13,360
Heiji told me that it was more delicious if the eggs are mixed.

385
00:23:16,360 --> 00:23:18,159
I told you!

386
00:23:18,160 --> 00:23:19,560
Mixing the eggs in the porridge make them taste better.

387
00:23:27,860 --> 00:23:30,859
"Novelist Fumie Masuko arrested" -You're really going for it, aren't you?

